22|## ðŸš€ Key Improvements
23|1.  **Token Reduction**: **~95-97%**. By moving visual heavy-lifting to Snipaste and local OCR, we have eliminated the "Token Black Hole" of browser screenshots.
24|2.  **Velocity Boost**: **6x Speedup**. Static Markdown reading and local image analysis are significantly faster than waiting for browser rendering and multi-turn subagent reasoning.
25|3.  **Context Hygiene**: The chat log no longer gets bloated with massive base64 image data, keeping your active context focused strictly on logic and goals.
